title: Stonebridge Crossing - 3/2.5 Two Story - Built 2021
posting_body: ['Stonebridge Crossing - 3/2.5 TWO STORY - JARRELL, TX', 'Property Address', '205 Sunnymeade Lane | Jarrell, TX 76537', 'Available: 08/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Niki Prekas, License #564065, Gamma Realty, LLC DBA Red Kanguru', 'Description', 'AVAILABLE 8/1 IN JARRELL!', 'Beautiful, two-story home with three beds and two and a half baths built in 2021.', 'Stonebridge Crossing is conveniently located right off of I-35 allowing residents to get anywhere they need or want to go quickly.', 'Residents at this community enjoy living near major employers, local schools, great shopping and dining venues and all of the exciting attractions that Austin has to offer.', 'Residents at Stonebridge Crossing enjoy incredible community amenities.', 'Inside this beautiful community, residents enjoy a park with a children’s playground and covered picnic pavilion with barbeque pits perfect for grilling out with your friends and neighbors.', 'Schools:', 'Jarrell Elementary: 1615 County Rd 313, Jarrell Tx 76537', 'Igo Elementary: 1601 County Rd 314, Jarrell Tx 76537', 'Jarrell Middle School:101 E Avenue F, Jarrell Tx 76537', 'Jarrell High School: 1100 FM 487, Jarrell Tx 76537', 'Qualifications:', '3 X the rent in gross income', 'No housing debt (broken lease/evictions/late pays)', 'No Felonies or violent/drug misdemeanors', 'Pets: Breed restrictions- max 2', 'Credit is case by case-owner prefers over 600.', 'If under 600 please let me know', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 3BD/2.5BA', 'Square Feet: 1,428', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,849.00', 'Available: 08/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $45.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,849.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
